Localization.Name: Virgil
Localization.Description:
High-end Commercial and Personal armor manufacturer. Aside from combat uses, they build systems for heavy commercial and mining applications.

Models: Achilles PDS (Heavy Combat Armor)

Zeus System (Titan Armor)

Localization.Name: Warden Backpack Epoque
Localization.Description:
Item Type: Heavy Backpack
Carrying Capacity: 150K µSCU
Core Compatibility: Heavy

This hard backpack from Virgil, Ltd. makes travel easy. Whether you need a place to carry your weapons or you've decided to bring some extra rations along for a long journey, this backpack was designed to handle any occasion. The interior features a generous, closeable pocket to keep your small items from falling out of place.

The Epoque edition features a navy and black coloring, finished with baroque gold detailing.
